Android tools to compile EasyRPG for Android devices

Specific building requirements for Linux :

    autoconf 
    mercurial 

1. Open « 4_build_android_port » and give to « KEYSTORE_PATH » and « KEYSTORE_PASSWORD » the value of your keystore’s path and password
2. Run « 0_build_everything.sh »
3. Open the Player/builds/android folder with Eclipse

NB : Complete the mips compilation could cause compilation.
We advise you to :
1) git clone https://github.com/EasyRPG/Player.git
2) desactivate mips compilation (which can cause problem) in « Player/builds/android/jni/Application.mk » in the APP_ABI variable